Installation of Evolution in Debian jessie 8.9 amd64

Packages
========
evolution-mapi - Exchange support for the Evolution groupware suite

1. Install via evolution-mapi and evolution-mapi-dbg packages:
covellite:~# aptitude install evolution-mapi evolution-mapi-dbg
The following NEW packages will be installed:
  evolution{a} evolution-common{a} evolution-data-server{a} 
